        <prompt>This trend most directly reflected the Progressive Era goal of:</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Efficient government</option>
            <option letter="b">Economic regulation</option>
            <option letter="c">Social justice</option>
            <option letter="d">Moral reform</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The decline of political machines following government reorganization reflected the Progressive goal of making government more efficient and professional.</explanation>
